{"tid":1933534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會選舉協調の最可靠簡單方法: 區議員牽引配票","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T10:34:51.000Z","uid":57677,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8a685ad22fc45ac8e739f1e8d89754410d13372f","tid":1933534,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"如果立法會選舉真係想協調得到嘅話，唔係無辦法，就係學中聯辦嘅做法--------<span style=\"color: red;\">配票 ! </span><br />\n<br />\n從區議會選舉，可以獲得準確的票數分佈資訊，從而為立法會選票配票所用。區選與立選相隔不足一年，而且個數據精細到選區level。區議員日常同街坊接觸，比起透過網上平台配票，更有信服力。數據又係現成嘅，又唔使怕五毛搞搞震、俾人hack之類。<br />\n<br />\n按此，可以推算出每個票站嘅嘅黃色選民比例，用區議會選區為單位配票：每個黃色區議員，喺自己所屬果一區，宣傳按機制所推舉嘅民主派立法會候選人。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有部分選民係唔會跟足配票，但可以喺計算時計入allowance與走盞位。"},{"pid":"9411b240b877c0e6ed766baf18d1557c1c7e6e13","tid":1933534,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ac10ab41352fe7e6a1fbd04426daf17436e6ac","tid":1933534,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"ce282289c6f48719aba2b69a9915dfca30082172","tid":1933534,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"f5ca76bcb1c1c45cd3d785732990c17677070c16","tid":1933534,"uid":205927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想贏呀"},{"pid":"5772f4d66cfdbd8309c210e3c757d75987862e25","tid":1933534,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ca76bcb1c1c45cd3d785732990c17677070c16","tid":1933534,"uid":205927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想贏呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202